<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="idbbd01454-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa" identifier="/us/usc/t42/s2000ff–10"><num value="2000ff–10">§ 2000ff–10.</num><heading> Regulations</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">Not later than 1 year after <date date="2008-05-21">May 21, 2008</date>, the Commission shall issue final regulations to carry out this chapter.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="idbbd01455-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa">(<ref href="/us/pl/110/233/tII/s211">Pub. L. 110–233, title II, § 211</ref>, <date date="2008-05-21">May 21, 2008</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/122/920">122 Stat. 920</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
<notes type="uscNote" id="idbbd01456-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa">
<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" role="crossHeading" topic="statutoryNotes" id="idbbd01457-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa"><heading class="centered"><b>Statutory Notes and Related Subsidiaries</b></heading></note>
<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" topic="effectiveDate" id="idbbd01458-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa"><heading class="centered smallCaps">Effective Date</heading><p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">Section effective 18 months after <date date="2008-05-21">May 21, 2008</date>, see <ref href="/us/pl/110/233/s213">section 213 of Pub. L. 110–233</ref>, set out as a note under <ref href="/us/usc/t42/s2000ff">section 2000ff of this title</ref>.</p>
</note>
